TALIESIN: Have fun you guys, I'll be on a beach
next week, but-- it's okay, I'll be, I'll try--

03:36:06.517 --> 03:36:08.725
LIAM: Where're you going, brainiac?

03:36:08.725 --> 03:36:10.869
TALIESIN: To Hawaii.

